Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:01.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:03.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:05.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:08.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:16.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the castle where\NNaraku's baby sleeps,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:19.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango reunites with\nher younger brother, Kohaku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guilt that cannot be erased,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:24.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}as well as tragic memories and heartache\nare about to be reawakened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:05.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The birds are dwindling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.05,0:02:09.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lady, please bear it\nfor just a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:10.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:14.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lady, we will be saved, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:20.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, it is because\nof you that we were saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And this child is without\na single scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:29.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're just a kid, but you did\na fine job, Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You will be rewarded later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:35.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:51.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My lady!\NThis way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:54.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:55.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:57.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:02:59.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}take the child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:02.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And kill everyone around you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Answer! Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:10.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why must I kill these people?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you gone mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this terrible feeling\NI have?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take the child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:46.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And kill everyone around you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... I don't want to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:06.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:20.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:29.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:34.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who....{\i0} Who is controlling\nyour heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:51.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's that lady...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:01.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}weren't killed by the birds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:39.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kanna? You were in\nthis castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? That's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's Hakudoshi's counterpart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? You're telling me\nto get Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:55.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:58.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kanna's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:03.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Half-demon! I'll put an end to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:10.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I'm gonna kill you on this spot\nand put an end to your evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:25.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is her barrier just as strong\nas Naraku's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:28.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If even Inuyasha's Tetsusaiga\ncan't break through it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, we have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silly girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:35.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Save me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:43.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay back!\NI can handle her by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The birds are starting to gather!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It must mean that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,they've sucked all the blood\nfrom the humans in that castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:53.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I expected more resistance\nfrom a castle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that is connected\nwith Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:07:00.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it seems it was\njust an ordinary human castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ordinary human castle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:05.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Kohaku is in this castle...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No doubt under Naraku's orders.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:12.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm withdrawing for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:14.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your life has been extended\nfor a while, half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:15.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:21.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up! Taking the human blood\nback to the nest is more important!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:40.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wind....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:42.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:50.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:51.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She got {\i1}away....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Sango?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You did it again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:12.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does she mean?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- What was that just now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:33.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who? Who is she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:00.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who am I?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:05.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}l- I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:13.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:37.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I killed my father and\neveryone else...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}with these hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:50.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember... everything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:03.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I killed my father and\nthe rest of the demon slayers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}with my own hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I even hurt Sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:15.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm supposed to have\ndied on that day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku, you're trembling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:30.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You want to forget\nthe terrible thing you've done?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forget then. Forget everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:38.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And work for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why you...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:22.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes! What do you think\nyou're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't care if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if we both die,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll get him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:50.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Sango!\N- Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not the work\nof the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:04.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:07.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:10.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did Kohaku go away again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:15.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I couldn't go after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:19.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were covered in blood...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:40.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I did take Kohaku away\nfrom Naraku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:44.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know how to free his heart\nfrom Naraku's grasp...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:51.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:56.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could... with my very own hands...\nkill Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:12:59.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The birds are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are we saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are survivors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:12.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Kohaku, where are you?!\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:22.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh {\i1}yes....{\i0} He worked with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:25.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We were saved by Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:27.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:31.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He protected us and\nfought off the demon-birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:34.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He looked like such an innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks to him, we're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:37.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:41.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:48.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku is a kind boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He really isn't one who\ncould do something like {\i1}that....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:57.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, I know it's difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but can you describe\nexactly what you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:24.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since Kohaku was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:26.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku must be connected\nin some way to that castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I rushed to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:38.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku was about to kill\na woman holding a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:39.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:40.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:43.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}baby....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iooked like Naraku's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:48.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:52.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right! That baby looked\njust like Naraku's infant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:56.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So that's the connection\nbetween Naraku and the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:58.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:07.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What were you doing\nat that castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why was that baby\nat that castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:19.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So was Naraku hiding his baby\nat a human castle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:23.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever the case,\none thing is certain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That baby is very special\nto Naraku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:30.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku, weren't you given\neven a clue
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,about who that baby is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:34.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:35.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Don't you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:49.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's Hakudoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The counterpart of that\nbaby you were with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:55.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:59.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why was the baby\nsplit in two?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:03.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}With one hidden in\na human castle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:11.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This one doesn't have a heart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:18.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That baby is Hakudoshi's heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:20.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or maybe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku's heart?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:25.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:28.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:44.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the direction that\NPrincess Abi went.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I don't even pick up\nthe scent of the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:55.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no sign of them\nin this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:17:00.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, the sun is still high\nin the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go a bit further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:02.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:34.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What will we do from now, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If Princess Abi has turned traitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:40.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,even if we find the nest, there's\nno guarantee that it'll lead to Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:42.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:47.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is after the human blood\nthat Princess Abi is collecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:48.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:51.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku intends to use human blood
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:54.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to cross into the other world\nwhere the Sacred Jewel fragment is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:59.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We still don't know how\nhe's going to do that, {\i1}though....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:08.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:11.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it okay to leave\NSango alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:12.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:19.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango's been so down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She must be worried about Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next time I see Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:31.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he has committed more sins...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:33.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}what will I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:36.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can I save Kohaku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:41.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:45.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0} Can I stay by you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:56.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to see you suffer.\NIs there something I can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:00.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,just stay here with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:04.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:12.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, he casually put his arm\naround her shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:13.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:15.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's not stroking her butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:16.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nope, her shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:18.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are so ignorant, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:19.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku may be a lecher,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but even he knows\nthere's a time and place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:25.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But didn't they promise\nto marry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango wouldn't get\nmad any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are really dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:31.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if you love someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:37.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you fall out of love if that person\nkeeps being insensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:41.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! But if Miroku stops\nacting like a lecher, what's left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:43.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe just his Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:47.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Sango.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:48.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't stroke your butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, keep your hands\noff for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:16.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mother, I attacked the castle,\nbut Naraku did not appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:21.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So instead, the birds sucked\nall the blood out of the humans there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:26.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks to you, the poison\nin my body has been diluted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But do not let your\nguard down, Princess Abi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:34.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm certain that the castle you attacked\nis connected to Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the proof of that {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:40.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the barrier around this nest\nis gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:41.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:46.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Naraku had hidden this nest\nby putting up a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though we never asked him\nto do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:51.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You think he's going to try something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That half-demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:14.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:34.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I smell the birds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are we close to the nest?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:48.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They are Kikyo's shikigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:51.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You {\i1}two....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:56.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:57.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:00.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:48.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I reunite with Kikyo,\nbut she has not completely healed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.72,0:23:50.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's impossible!\NYou wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:52.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then give this to {\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:55.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But whether she can use it\ndepends on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.26,0:23:57.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One arrow is entrusted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:23:58.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:02.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Naraku battles\NPrincess Abi's mother, Tekkei,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:05.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and opens the path that connects\nthis world to the next!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:07.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:09.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"The Demon Linked\nwith the Netherworld"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:12.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The broken barrier...\nis a trap laid by Naraku!
